        "type": "AcceptanceCriteria",
        "description": "Validation geometry and operating envelope must match COU. Species differences must be documented with quantified correction and uncertainty. Achieved: identical geometry; bovine-to-human correction factor 1.07 ± 18% propagated through UQ."
