      "rationale": "Simulation setup was reviewed by a second qualified analyst; checklist covers boundary condition assignment, material property selection, turbulence model selection, and hemolysis model parameter entry. Two minor parameter entry errors were caught and corrected during review. Use error risk is rated low after review; no residual errors identified.",
