        "type": "AcceptanceCriteria",
        "description": "All inputs with CV > 10% must have documented distributions with source references and sensitivity analysis identification. Achieved: C (CV 15%) and RBC fragility (CV 18%) documented with meta-analysis sources and identified as primary drivers; conservative bias supports acceptance."
