        "type": "AcceptanceCriteria",
        "description": "Minimum 3 replicates per operating point required. Power analysis must be documented. Achieved: 3–4 replicates per point; 80% power at 20% shift documented; primary uncertainty identified as model-form, not measurement scatter."
